</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/HTVcYib4IE4" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/02/airport-auto/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=airport-auto</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>Beats Fit Pro 運動型耳機    Apple H1 晶片 + 空間音訊</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/J7GsSBkOIpE/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 02 Nov 2021 10:00:53 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple H1 晶片]]></category><category><![CDATA[Beats Fit Pro]]></category><category><![CDATA[無線耳機]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1069232</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Apple 旗下音樂品牌 Beats 繼推出具備主動降噪技術的真無線耳機 Beats Studio Buds  [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Apple 旗下音樂品牌 Beats 繼推出具備主動降噪技術的真無線耳機 Beats Studio Buds 後，近日宣佈將推出針對運動訓練的真無線耳機 Beats Fit Pro。Beats Fit Pro 將搭載 Apple H1 晶片，與第三代 AirPods 一樣，具備基於頭部追蹤的空間音訊功能。預計 11 月初在美國上市、 12 月初在中國大陸推出，香港則將在 2022 年初推出。</span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/BeatsFitPro_4FAM_Lifestyle_0036_WEB_v4.0.png.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1069248" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/BeatsFitPro_4FAM_Lifestyle_0036_WEB_v4.0.png-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/BeatsFitPro_4FAM_Lifestyle_0036_WEB_v4.0.png-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/BeatsFitPro_4FAM_Lifestyle_0036_WEB_v4.0.png-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/BeatsFitPro_4FAM_Lifestyle_0036_WEB_v4.0.png.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/158938-headphones-news-beats-fit-pro-official-image2-bxny3wxkbk.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1069252" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/158938-headphones-news-beats-fit-pro-official-image2-bxny3wxkbk-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/158938-headphones-news-beats-fit-pro-official-image2-bxny3wxkbk-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/158938-headphones-news-beats-fit-pro-official-image2-bxny3wxkbk-768x511.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/158938-headphones-news-beats-fit-pro-official-image2-bxny3wxkbk.jpg 946w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/5949516.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1069249" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/5949516-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/5949516-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/5949516-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/5949516-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/5949516-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/5949516.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/https-hk.hypebeast.com-files-2021-11-beats-fit-pro-earbuds-release-info-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1069250" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/https-hk.hypebeast.com-files-2021-11-beats-fit-pro-earbuds-release-info-1-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/https-hk.hypebeast.com-files-2021-11-beats-fit-pro-earbuds-release-info-1-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/https-hk.hypebeast.com-files-2021-11-beats-fit-pro-earbuds-release-info-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/https-hk.hypebeast.com-files-2021-11-beats-fit-pro-earbuds-release-info-1.jpg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">作為針對高強度運動訓練的產品，Beats Fit Pro 加入了耳翼設計，聲稱在高度運動訓練也不會掉落。最大的賣點在於其支援會「不斷進行即時調整」的主動降噪，每秒可調整達 200 次的主動降噪，並可單按耳機「b」圖案上的按鍵切換至通透模式。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1069235 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/29BE5A37-FAB9-4DCF-889B-C2953715E2D1-694x462.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/29BE5A37-FAB9-4DCF-889B-C2953715E2D1-694x462.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/29BE5A37-FAB9-4DCF-889B-C2953715E2D1-1280x852.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/29BE5A37-FAB9-4DCF-889B-C2953715E2D1-768x511.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/29BE5A37-FAB9-4DCF-889B-C2953715E2D1-1536x1022.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/29BE5A37-FAB9-4DCF-889B-C2953715E2D1-2048x1363.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/29BE5A37-FAB9-4DCF-889B-C2953715E2D1.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">在 Apple H1 晶片的幫助下，Beats Fit Pro 也支援免提 Siri、一鍵配對、自動切換裝置、音訊共享以及 iOS 裡最新的 Find My 工具。和新一代 AirPods 一樣，Beats Fit Pro 有適應性 EQ、空間音訊和動態頭部追蹤，用戶可在手機上進行耳塞的配戴測試。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br /><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1069236" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/C917BBD5-3669-47C9-A410-C16A86B7CE95-694x469.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="469" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/C917BBD5-3669-47C9-A410-C16A86B7CE95-694x469.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/C917BBD5-3669-47C9-A410-C16A86B7CE95-768x519.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/C917BBD5-3669-47C9-A410-C16A86B7CE95.jpeg 1193w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><br /></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">在開啟降噪或透音模式的情況下，Beats Fit Pro 耳機本體續航力最長可達 6 個小時。收納盒有 21 小時的額外電力。在全程使用自適應 EQ 的前提下，耳機本體的使用時長能增加到 7 小時，配合充電盒綜合續航力為 30 小時。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Beats Fit Pro 在美國的售價為 US$200（約 HK$1,560），即日開始預售，中國大陸則由 12 月 7 日開始預售。2022 年初在香港推出，售價將在稍後公佈。</span></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_74813"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KZZB-QSsEFg?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://techcrunch.com/2021/11/01/beats-fit-pro-review-ahead-of-the-pack/">Techcrunch</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
