</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/RirE77c0MLc" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/02/apps-immigration-tower/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=apps-immigration-tower</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>【評測】Acer Aspire Vero 全環保物料筆電外形　手感　功能初步評測</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/lOqb1RI2jus/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Edward]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 02 Nov 2021 04:35:15 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[流動電腦]]></category><category><![CDATA[評測]]></category><category><![CDATA[acer]]></category><category><![CDATA[aspire]]></category><category><![CDATA[Vero]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1068420</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>去到 2021 年，不少科技品牌推出新產品時，除了注重新功能及設計外，亦愈來愈注重環保元素，希望透過機身用料、 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>去到 2021 年，不少科技品牌推出新產品時，除了注重新功能及設計外，亦愈來愈注重環保元素，希望透過機身用料、設計、甚至包裝物料，為保護地球出一分力。今日 Acer 就舉行了發佈會，宣佈推出採用全環保物料製造的 Aspire Vero 筆電，就讓 Edward 帶大家到現場看看這部全環保筆電有甚麼特別吧。</p><h2>火山泥色機身用色特別手感佳</h2><p>Acer 最新推出的 Aspire Vero 筆電，屬於 Desktop Replacement 類別的筆電。它最特別的地方就是機身設計，它的外殼，由機身到鍵帽都用上了 PCR 塑料，即是用後的回收樹脂物料，這種物料不只環保，而且具可持續性，可有效減少垃圾堆填的物料製造。另外，機身設計上為了方便維修、升級及回收，不但螺絲選用標準大小，機殼亦不使用油漆，令筆電他日棄置時，機身不會有有害物質而破壞環境，由此可見，整部筆電設計，確實貫徹了其環保元素。至於用色方面，它用上了火山泥灰的綠色，當中更包含不少黃點，這種用色配搭在筆電上十分少有，確實有種眼前一亮的感覺，加上沒有刻意打磨的機面設計，少許凹凸花紋令使用時摸上去手感十分不錯，設計絕對值得一讚。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05643-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068425" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05643-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05643-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05643-1-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05643-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05643-1-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05643-1.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05648.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068432" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05648-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05648-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05648-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05648-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05648-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05648.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲這部就是 Acer 最新推出，採用全環保物料製造的 Aspire Vero 手提電腦。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05649.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068433" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05649-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05649-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05649-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05649-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05649-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05649.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機底印著 For Planet Earth，已標明希望為環保出一分力。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05644.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068426" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05644-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05644-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05644-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05644-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05644-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05644.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05633.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068427" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05633-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05633-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05633-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05633-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05633-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05633.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05634.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068428" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05634-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05634-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05634-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05634-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05634-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05634.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05635.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068429" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05635-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05635-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05635-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05635-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05635-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05635.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機身沒有使用任何漆油，只以雕刻方式將標誌刻在機身，減少漆油的有毒物質，在有朝一日棄置電腦時對環境所造成的傷害，確實十分有心。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05632.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068430" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05632-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05632-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05632-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05632-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05632-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05632.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05647.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068431" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05647-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05647-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05647-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05647-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05647-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05647.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機身採用猶如火山泥般的灰綠色，配合黃色墊位及點點，設計十分特別搶眼。</p><h2>鍵盤按打舒服設計特別</h2><p>至於鍵盤方面，Aspire Vero 內建了 15.6 吋筆電的標準尺寸鍵盤佈局，亦內建了數字鍵盤，配置十分齊全。另外，大家可以見到 Vero 鍵盤的 R、E 兩鍵是採用鏡面反射的打印設計，這並非是錯體，而只是官方希望以鏡像文字強調環保的 3R 概念：Reduce（減量）、Reuse（重複使用）及 Recycle（回收再造），由此可見 Vero 確實是由內至外均展現出環保概念的筆電。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05637.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068434" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05637-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05637-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05637-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05637-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05637-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05637.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲鍵盤按鍵大細適中，鍵程亦夠深，長時間打字都算舒服。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05636.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068436" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05636-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05636-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05636-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05636-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05636-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05636.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲鍵盤上的 R、E 兩鍵採用鏡像式設計，亦是標明注重環保的一個元素。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05638.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068435" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05638-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05638-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05638-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05638-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05638-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05638.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲鍵盤內建了數字鍵盤，方便用家輸入數字。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05640.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068437" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05640-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05640-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05640-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05640-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05640-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05640.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲觸控板面積夠大，多指操控亦十分方便。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05639.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068438" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05639-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05639-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05639-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05639-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05639-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05639.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲觸控板左上角設有指紋辨識器，登入系統更加方便。</p><h2>規格足夠應付日常所需</h2><p>至於硬件規格方面，Acer Aspire Vero 雖然並非旗艦機款，但也內建了最新第 11 代 Intel Core i5 / i7 處理器、Intel Iris Xe 圖像處理晶片、8GB + 8GB DDR4 RAM、1TB PCIe NVMe SSD 及 15.6 吋 1080p IPS 防反光霧面熒幕，並已預載了 Windows 11 作業系統，這個配置已足夠應該用家日常所需。另外，雖然它並非輕薄機款，但重量也不過是 1.8kg，加上官方表示使用時間可長達 9.5 小時，即使打個折扣也應用到 7 小時以上，即使要在家在不接駁電源的情況下隨處使用，也不用擔心不夠電用，最少用來煲 4、5 集劇集亦無問題。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05650.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068439" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05650-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05650-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05650-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05650-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05650-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05650.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲內建了最新第 11 代 Intel Core i5 / i7 處理器及 Intel Iris Xe 圖像處理晶片，雖然並非旗艦級配置，但已足夠應付多數用家日常生活所需。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_7830.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068440" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_7830-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_7830-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_7830-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_7830-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_7830-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_7830.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲內建 1TB PCIe NVMe SSD，並預設已界開兩個 partition，方便用家將資料及程式分開擺放，十分體貼。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_7831.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068441" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_7831-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_7831-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_7831-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_7831-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_7831-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_7831.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲熒幕解像度為 1920 x 1080，並採用防反光設計，長時間瀏覽雙眼亦不會易感疲倦。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05641.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068442" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05641-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05641-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05641-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05641-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05641-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05641.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05642.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068443" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05642-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05642-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05642-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05642-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05642-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05642.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在機身左右側，內建了 3 個 USB-A 插槽、1 個 USB-C 插槽、HDMI 輸出、LAN 插槽及 3.5mm 耳機咪高風混合插孔，端子十分齊全，作為 Desktop Replacement 完全適合。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_7828.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068444" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_7828-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_7828-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_7828-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_7828-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_7828-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_7828.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲預載了最新 Windows 11 作業系統，令市場預載 Win 11 的筆電選擇又多一部。</p><h2>即日發佈定價抵玩</h2><p>至於發售詳情方面，Acer Aspire Vero 將會即日推出發售，售價為 $8,698 起，以擁有特別設計元素的筆電來說，這個定價算是抵玩。至於整體表現如何，筆者稍後將會借得此機，有興趣的讀者就不要錯過了。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05630.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068424" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05630-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05630-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05630-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05630-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05630-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/DSC05630.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
